01:04:06,100 --> 01:04:09,090
So the air would get to the tattoo afterwards

558
01:04:17,130 --> 01:04:19,130
Do you think I'm pathetic?

559
01:04:21,180 --> 01:04:23,090
..just a little..

560
01:04:34,110 --> 01:04:36,120
Do you hate me?

561
01:04:37,260 --> 01:04:39,230
..just a little..

562
01:04:43,220 --> 01:04:46,050
