574
01:07:39,070 --> 01:07:42,090
What will I think then?

575
01:07:42,290 --> 01:07:45,030
I will have nothing left,

576
01:07:45,060 --> 01:07:47,250
Care about nothing, and live without blame

577
01:07:49,040 --> 01:07:53,290
In the future, the tattoo and split tongue

578
01:07:54,020 --> 01:07:56,050
will surely have no meaning at all

579
01:09:13,200 --> 01:09:15,230
I wonder if should I quit tattooing

580
01:09:19,170 --> 01:09:23,000
Get a girl, live a normal life. Like Ama

581
01:09:25,070 --> 01:09:28,050
Do you have to give up tattooing to do that?

582
01:09:29,000 --> 01:09:31,070
I mean start a new life

583
01:09:33,170 --> 01:09:35,200
I've tattooed the best kirin I can.

584
01:09:40,030 --> 01:09:43,160
I have no feelings of regret

585
01:09:51,000 --> 01:09:54,050
The dragon and kirin dancing on my back

586
01:09:54,080 --> 01:09:56,200
will never be separated from me

587
01:09:57,180 --> 01:10:00,150
We decided on each other

588
01:10:00,180 --> 01:10:03,160
This relationship can't be betrayed

589
01:10:04,010 --> 01:10:08,060
After all, they can't go anywhere if they don't have eyes

590
01:10:15,130 --> 01:10:18,090
