595
01:10:32,050 --> 01:10:35,220
And even though I wanted to respond to him..

596
01:10:35,250 --> 01:10:39,000
every time, the loathing I felt for myself..

597
01:10:39,030 --> 01:10:41,250
eventually pushed me back to drinking again

598
01:10:42,060 --> 01:10:44,190
Anyhow, the absence of light

599
