my life, my future and inside my head was total darkness

600
01:10:52,130 --> 01:10:55,270
The only time i could sense any true feeling

601
01:10:56,000 --> 01:10:58,210
was when I felt pain.

602
01:11:01,140 --> 01:11:05,230
Lui, do you ever think you want to die?

603
