The person you are calling...

684
01:23:30,100 --> 01:23:32,190
- Excuse me
- Yes?

685
01:23:33,000 --> 01:23:35,230
Can I report a missing person other than a relative here?

686
01:23:35,260 --> 01:23:37,090
Yes you can

687
01:23:38,150 --> 01:23:39,260
Well?

688
01:23:41,050 --> 01:23:42,050
well?

689
01:23:43,020 --> 01:23:44,020
The persons name?

690
01:24:00,250 --> 01:24:03,160
I don't know Ama's full name

691
01:24:04,090 --> 01:24:08,260
I can't report a person as missing
if I don't even know his name

692
01:24:20,210 --> 01:24:22,170
What's Ama's name?

693
01:24:22,230 --> 01:24:25,160
Huh? What's the hurry?

694
01:24:27,290 --> 01:24:31,170
He hasn't come home.
I wan't to report him missing.

