01:24:32,060 --> 01:24:37,000
You don't know his name?

696
01:24:37,110 --> 01:24:38,260
I don't

697
01:24:39,000 --> 01:24:40,130
But you're living together.

698
01:24:40,160 --> 01:24:42,080
So what?

699
01:24:44,020 --> 01:24:45,290
Don't cry

700
01:24:49,100 --> 01:24:52,250
Didn't you ever see a name
plate or letter or something?

701
