Ama didn't have anything like a name plate.

702
01:24:57,110 --> 01:24:59,230
The mailbox was always full of leaflets

703
01:24:59,260 --> 01:25:01,240
'cos he never opened it

704
01:25:02,050 --> 01:25:04,210
Did he go to work as usual yesterday?

705
01:25:06,050 --> 01:25:08,160
