706
01:25:08,190 --> 01:25:12,190
Right, he left for work as usual  but
didn't come home.

707
01:25:13,120 --> 01:25:17,060
Why are you so upset after just one day?

708
01:25:17,180 --> 01:25:19,110
It will be fine

709
01:25:21,030 --> 01:25:24,190
He hasn't been home for 1 day, don't panic so much

710
01:25:24,220 --> 01:25:25,240
He's not a kid

711
01:25:26,030 --> 01:25:27,220
