712
01:25:27,250 --> 01:25:30,160
He hasn't spent 1 night away from home

713
01:25:30,190 --> 01:25:32,040
He was once 30 minutes late leaving work

714
01:25:32,070 --> 01:25:34,090
But he called me so I wouldn't worry.
That's how he is.

715
01:25:35,030 --> 01:25:36,080
I know..

716
01:25:37,240 --> 01:25:42,060
Ama, might have killed someone

717
01:25:45,090 --> 01:25:48,180
The police said he was a Yakuza member

718
01:25:48,210 --> 01:25:50,200
I told him not to

719
01:25:50,240 --> 01:25:52,240
I told Ama to ignore him

720
01:25:52,280 --> 01:25:55,230
Ama beat him up but..

721
01:25:55,270 --> 01:25:59,020
I never thought he would die

722
01:25:59,180 --> 01:26:01,130
Even when I saw it on the news

723
01:26:01,160 --> 01:26:05,000
I didn't really think it was the same person

724
01:26:06,050 --> 01:26:10,100
I was sure it was a different person
It couldn't have been about Ama.

725
01:26:15,090 --> 01:26:19,090
If we report him missing to the police,
they may arrest him

726
01:26:22,050 --> 01:26:26,000
If he knows about all of this and has gone on the run.

727
01:26:28,070 --> 01:26:30,210
If he thinks we don't know about this,

728
01:26:30,240 --> 01:26:31,280
