without telling us.

729
01:26:32,010 --> 01:26:34,110
I'm worried about him

730
01:26:36,220 --> 01:26:40,290
It's too hard, not knowing where
he is or what he's doing

731
01:26:43,150 --> 01:26:48,050
I don't think Ama would run away on his own

732
01:26:49,130 --> 01:26:53,010
If he was going to, he would have taken me with him

733
01:26:53,050 --> 01:26:57,000
