734
01:27:02,250 --> 01:27:04,090
Ok

735
01:27:06,080 --> 01:27:07,220
Let's go

736
01:27:21,040 --> 01:27:23,160
Why do you have a photo of him?

737
01:27:24,010 --> 01:27:25,060
Ah,

738
01:27:26,120 --> 01:27:30,130
When I did his tattoo, we took lots of photos..

739
01:27:30,220 --> 01:27:34,060
Amada Kazunori, is it?

740
01:27:34,220 --> 01:27:36,040
Yes

741
01:27:44,020 --> 01:27:47,010
He's not called Ama Deus after all?

742
01:27:52,020 --> 01:27:54,100
Are you ok?

743
01:28:19,090 --> 01:28:21,140
Ama?

744
01:28:49,010 --> 01:28:51,090
What's happened?

745
01:28:54,150 --> 01:28:57,190
Why did you leave me behind?

746
01:29:09,120 --> 01:29:12,290
Why did you go before me?

747
01:29:15,270 --> 01:29:19,220
Didn't you say I meant everything to you?

748
01:29:22,050 --> 01:29:26,060
Why have you left me alone?

749
01:29:28,110 --> 01:29:30,190
Why?

750
01:29:31,260 --> 01:29:33,160
Why?

751
01:29:58,170 --> 01:29:59,280
What are you doing?

752
01:30:00,150 --> 01:30:02,290
Hey, stick your tongue out!

753
01:30:04,090 --> 01:30:08,220
Isn't that a zero? Weren't you at 4 yesterday?

754
01:30:10,190 --> 01:30:11,190
Stop it

755
01:30:17,040 --> 01:30:18,030
Take it out

756
01:30:24,230 --> 01:30:27,040
You'll stretch it too far

757
01:30:38,120 --> 01:30:41,100
When I get to 00 I can split my tongue

758
01:30:42,050 --> 01:30:46,000
I know, I know..

759
01:30:51,040 --> 01:30:52,270
Ama..

760
01:30:54,060 --> 01:30:58,250
