763
01:31:12,040 --> 01:31:15,030
"Just a little further"

764
01:31:17,020 --> 01:31:18,220
I know..

765
01:31:21,070 --> 01:31:23,050
that's what he would say

766
01:31:26,270 --> 01:31:29,090
He'd be so happy

767
01:31:42,110 --> 01:31:46,010
The person you are calling is not in range
of our signal

768
01:31:46,070 --> 01:31:49,010
or the phone is turned off, and cannot be reached.

769
01:31:57,270 --> 01:31:59,030
Hey

770
01:32:00,230 --> 01:32:02,170
Do you know where Ama works?

771
01:32:02,200 --> 01:32:05,150
What? You don't know?

772
01:32:05,230 --> 01:32:07,080
I don't know.

773
01:32:08,270 --> 01:32:12,240
We didn't know anything about each other

774
01:32:15,110 --> 01:32:16,240
He works at a second hand clothes shop

775
01:32:18,030 --> 01:32:20,160
You really didn't tell each other anything huh.

776
01:32:22,260 --> 01:32:24,290
Did you discuss anything?

777
01:32:42,240 --> 01:32:46,040
Hey, It's me.  It's about Ama

778
01:32:47,170 --> 01:32:48,220
Ah..

779
01:32:49,270 --> 01:32:54,040
He's not been in? What about yesterday?

780
01:32:55,290 --> 01:32:58,170
If you find out anything, let me know ok?

781
01:33:05,230 --> 01:33:08,230
He went to work as normal yesterday

782
01:33:10,200 --> 01:33:13,000
but didn't today.

783
01:33:14,170 --> 01:33:17,080
His boss is pretty angry.

784
01:33:20,080 --> 01:33:24,100
I know the people there

785
01:33:26,150 --> 01:33:29,070
They gave him a job without any questions

786
01:33:33,110 --> 01:33:36,020
Does Ama have any family?

787
01:33:38,190 --> 01:33:40,030
I don't know

788
01:33:41,210 --> 01:33:43,190
I think he has one parent

789
01:33:45,010 --> 01:33:49,180
He talked about his father once

790
01:33:49,260 --> 01:33:51,170
Oh

791
01:34:14,240 --> 01:34:18,270
What?
Nothing but beer

792
01:34:21,150 --> 01:34:23,210
It's ringing

793
01:34:25,280 --> 01:34:27,100
yes

794
01:34:29,050 --> 01:34:30,150
yes

795
01:34:34,090 --> 01:34:35,250
I see

796
01:34:36,220 --> 01:34:38,190
Yes, I understand.

797
01:34:57,030 --> 01:34:59,220
A body has been found in Yokosu.

798
01:35:01,130 --> 01:35:06,260
They don't know if it's Ama,
but there is a dragon tattoo

799
01:35:12,020 --> 01:35:15,110
They want us to go to the morgue
to identify the body

800
01:35:20,260 --> 01:35:22,040
Alright

801
01:36:15,220 --> 01:36:17,180
Ama is dead

802
01:36:17,220 --> 01:36:21,040
He had been strangled to death

803
01:36:21,110 --> 01:36:25,060
All over his body were cigarette burns

804
01:36:25,290 --> 01:36:29,260
every finger and toe nail had been pulled out

805
01:36:29,290 --> 01:36:33,280
