had been inserted into his penis.

806
01:36:34,060 --> 01:36:36,050
How should it be said?

807
01:36:36,080 --> 01:36:40,080
he was killed after being beaten and tortured.

808
01:36:40,110 --> 01:36:43,180
Like an object or a possession,

809
01:36:43,210 --> 01:36:47,200
he was played with and then killed

810
01:36:49,110 --> 01:36:51,260
Lui, I'm going now

811
01:36:53,220 --> 01:36:57,110
the last conversation we had

812
01:36:57,150 --> 01:36:59,140
I had my back to Ama

813
01:36:59,170 --> 01:37:02,080
I was thinking about meeting Shiba

814
01:37:02,170 --> 01:37:04,170
See you later

815
