817
01:37:45,280 --> 01:37:48,240
What? Am I being too pushy?

818
01:37:48,270 --> 01:37:50,080
Please excuse me

819
01:37:50,110 --> 01:37:54,070
Why did you come to the funeral when
you can't catch the killer?

820
01:37:54,100 --> 01:37:58,120
and you're saying I'm pushy?

821
01:37:58,210 --> 01:38:02,030
You don't have that authority

822
01:38:02,060 --> 01:38:03,070
So, what?

823
01:38:03,110 --> 01:38:07,090
So saying you can't catch his killer is ridiculous?

824
01:38:07,230 --> 01:38:11,110
You're not trying because Ama killed too!

825
01:38:11,210 --> 01:38:18,010
