Then everything will be settled

826
01:38:18,040 --> 01:38:20,220
Calm down
You're not making sense

827
01:38:20,250 --> 01:38:24,000
fuck off and die

828
01:38:56,010 --> 01:38:58,270
We'll look after the store together
for a while

829
01:38:59,170 --> 01:39:03,170
You have to take it easy
like the doctor said

830
01:39:29,140 --> 01:39:31,250
When I left Ama's room

831
01:39:31,280 --> 01:39:34,260
I went to live with Shiba

832
01:39:35,080 --> 01:39:40,130
He tried to comfort me many
times, but couldn't

833
01:39:41,080 --> 01:39:46,180
my lack of emotion meant he
couldn't even strangle me

834
01:40:03,100 --> 01:40:05,120
Hey, Shiba

835
01:40:07,070 --> 01:40:11,190
Ah, could you stop calling me Shiba?

836
01:40:13,230 --> 01:40:16,140
My name is Shiba Kizuki

837
01:40:17,250 --> 01:40:20,010
Sounds like a womans name, huh

838
01:40:22,230 --> 01:40:26,180
I don't know why but everybody
calls me Shiba

839
01:40:28,050 --> 01:40:30,030
What do you want me to call you?

840
01:40:30,080 --> 01:40:31,230
Kizuki is fine

841
01:40:32,260 --> 01:40:34,150
Kizuki

842
01:40:36,210 --> 01:40:37,240
What?

843
01:40:38,280 --> 01:40:42,080
You can't get any more in here

844
01:40:43,000 --> 01:40:46,080
Ah yeah, it's full

845
01:40:54,220 --> 01:40:59,020
Lui, is it ok if you
tell me your name?

846
01:41:00,020 --> 01:41:01,100
