847
01:41:01,130 --> 01:41:03,150
Yeah, I'm listening

848
01:41:05,100 --> 01:41:07,140
I'm Lui as in Louis Vuitton...

849
01:41:07,170 --> 01:41:09,270
Your real name

850
01:41:11,170 --> 01:41:13,150
Nakagawa Lui

851
01:41:14,220 --> 01:41:17,170
What is Lui short for?

852
01:41:20,100 --> 01:41:24,230
Lui, do you have any family?
Any parents?

853
01:41:26,250 --> 01:41:29,240
I may look like an orphan but

854
01:41:29,270 --> 01:41:31,260
I have parents

855
01:41:32,180 --> 01:41:35,260
