about normal things more often

860
01:42:03,040 --> 01:42:06,010
about family,

861
01:42:07,210 --> 01:42:12,110
about names, about age

862
01:42:14,160 --> 01:42:21,050
Ama was 18 years old and I
only found out at his funeral

863
01:42:24,060 --> 01:42:31,100
He was the first person younger
than me I ever hung around with

864
01:42:32,070 --> 01:42:35,170
and I only found that out now he's gone

865
01:42:36,220 --> 01:42:41,000
I wish I had realised that earlier
and talked with him about it

866
01:42:55,250 --> 01:43:03,190
The burns were all done with Marlboro
cigarettes, menthol flavoured

867
01:43:04,030 --> 01:43:06,290
Of course, we're making progress with
saliva samples too

868
01:43:12,080 --> 01:43:19,140
Also, the incense stick inserted
into the genitals

869
