was a kind called 'Ecstacy', musk
variety imported from America

870
01:43:25,080 --> 01:43:28,000
Surely incense is sold everywhere.

871
01:43:28,080 --> 01:43:33,220
Yes, but.. in this area that kind
is not widely available

872
