877
01:44:12,240 --> 01:44:15,230
He definately wasn't that way

878
01:44:17,100 --> 01:44:19,090
I see

879
01:45:02,260 --> 01:45:05,050
No use

880
01:45:05,240 --> 01:45:07,140
Oh.

881
01:45:45,280 --> 01:45:47,170
You should rest

882
01:46:45,140 --> 01:46:47,290
Where did you go? I was worried

883
01:46:48,180 --> 01:46:54,090
Ah, I went to buy incense.
I hate musk

884
01:46:59,040 --> 01:47:01,030
I bought coconut

885
01:47:20,180 --> 01:47:22,050
Whats up

886
01:47:22,080 --> 01:47:23,230
Nothing

887
01:47:23,260 --> 01:47:26,220
So Kizuki, you should grow your hair

888
01:47:26,260 --> 01:47:28,280
I like long hair

889
01:47:30,040 --> 01:47:34,170
Ok.. I wonder if I should
grow it once in a while

890
01:51:16,160 --> 01:51:23,160
The symbol of Ama's love for me,
became part of me

891
01:51:52,180 --> 01:51:57,190
Kizuki, I have one more request

892
01:51:58,030 --> 01:51:59,170
What is it?

893
01:52:04,130 --> 01:52:06,030
Are you sure about this?

894
01:52:21,030 --> 01:52:22,160
Ok

895
01:53:01,240 --> 01:53:06,210
At last I can say this tattoo has a deep meaning to me,

896
01:53:06,240 --> 01:53:09,200
for what my life has become.

897
01:53:09,230 --> 01:53:12,240
I finally gave my dragon and kirin their eyes

898
01:53:13,090 --> 01:53:15,080
I wonder if they will fly away?

899
01:53:15,210 --> 01:53:18,030
I don't know

900
01:53:38,060 --> 01:53:40,140
It's all ok.

901
01:53:40,170 --> 01:53:43,090
If Shiba killed Ama

902
01:53:43,120 --> 01:53:47,220
If Shiba raped Ama.. I accept it all.

903
01:56:24,130 --> 01:56:27,170
Is this all I wanted?

904
01:56:27,200 --> 01:56:31,120
This unsightly, gaping hole is all I needed?

905
01:57:40,200 --> 01:57:42,180
What are you doing?

906
01:57:43,240 --> 01:57:46,130
I am making a river inside of me

907
01:57:47,060 --> 01:57:48,110
Huh?

908
01:57:54,140 --> 01:57:56,050
I just had a wierd dream

909
01:57:57,220 --> 01:57:59,090
What sort?

910
01:58:02,210 --> 01:58:06,140
I was hanging out with a good
friend from a long time ago

911
01:58:07,180 --> 01:58:11,150
but I was really late for an appointment

912
01:58:12,170 --> 01:58:18,280
So my friend began to sing about his anger

913
